\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">&#183;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Estimated Capacity Setting: 1,850,000 – 2,000,000 Dth </span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">&#183;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Design Capacity: 2,344,656 Dth</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">&#183;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160;&#160; Posted Percentage: 79-85%</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Due to the potential impact to firm service, CGT encourages customers to monitor the scheduled volumes on the Operationally Available Capacity screen on Informational Postings, as nominations can fluctuate based on market conditions.&#160;</span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Reservation Charge Credits (RCCs) will be determined per the process set forth in the General Terms and Conditions, Section 40 of CGT’s FERC Gas Tariff (Tariff). By means of this notice, CGT is establishing the 7-day Average Usage Quantity to be the period of December 30, 2025 – January 5, 2026, pursuant to the provisions in the Tariff. </span></DIV><DIV style=\\\"padding-bottom:10pt;\\\" class=\\\"a53\\\"><span style=\\\"font-family:'calibri, sans-serif';\\\" class=\\\"a52\\\">Please contact your Customer Services Representative with any questions.</span></DIV></DIV></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></TD><TD WIDTH=\\\"100%\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"0\\\"></TD></TR><TR><TD WIDTH=\\\"0\\\" HEIGHT=\\\"100%\\\"></TD></TR></TABLE></DIV></DIV></body></html>\"}],\"temperature\":0.1,\"max_tokens\":2000,\"response_fo